======================================================================
 Class TSFleMem - Hold iteration-values for expand/reduce
 Sub-Class TSFleMem - Hold iteration-values for expand/reduce
 This class is used to save values if expand/reduce enters an
   embeded token. So no restriction about 'size' is given.
 ##TSFleMem (Eyecatcher)
